docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. * b8e64fc (origin/develop, develop) add name.txt * c95f89a Revert "add hello3.txt" * a4f36b3 remove hello2.txt * 0db7243 add hello3.txt * 4767ebd (HEAD -> main, tag: v1.0, origin/release/v1.0, origin/main, origin/HEAD, release/v1.0) add LICENSE * 203dddb (origin/feature/gitignore, feature/gitignore) add .gitignore,ignore .tmp * 36f5562 update hello.txt and add hello2.txt * 5f1cf8e (tag: v0.2, tag: v0.1, origin/hotfix/case, hotfix/case) hello.txt * 8ac995a chore: initial commit
